# MLDS 4.0 — MoneyLion Design System Reference

> **What this file is:** The single source of truth for all visual tokens, component specs, spacing, typography, and interaction patterns in the MoneyLion Design System. Every prototype, audit, and design recommendation should reference this file for exact values.
>
> **Related files:**
> - `company-context.md` — Vision, strategy, product surface, user segments, regulatory constraints (the "what and why" file)
> - `moneylion-project-instructions.md` — Design consulting role, voice/tone, UX principles, feedback frameworks
> - `moneylion-workflow-instructions.md` — Shorthand triggers (`/react`, `/audit`, etc.), response formats, session patterns
>
> **Figma source:** [MLDS 4.0](https://www.figma.com/design/SyfKKZyUM3cW4IunxIk8Bj/MLDS-4.0--Don-t-Use-fig)
> **Last updated:** March 2026

