## React Prototype Token Map

When building interactive prototypes (via `/react` or any JSX/HTML mockup), use these CSS custom properties. This ensures every prototype uses real MLDS values rather than approximations.

**Important:** Baton Turbo is not available via Google Fonts or CDN. For prototypes, use `'DM Sans', -apple-system, system-ui, sans-serif` as the closest web-safe substitute. Note this substitution in prototype output so stakeholders know the final product uses Baton Turbo.

### Light Mode (default for MoneyLion product screens)

```css
:root {
  /* Font */
  --font-family: 'DM Sans', -apple-system, system-ui, sans-serif;
  --font-weight-regular: 400;
  --font-weight-medium: 600;

  /* Background */
  --bg-primary: #F6F6F6;       /* Neutral-100 — screen bg */
  --bg-secondary: #FFFFFF;      /* Neutral-0 — card bg */
  --bg-tertiary: #F6F6F6;       /* Neutral-100 — nested surfaces */
  --bg-alt: #000000;            /* Neutral-1000 — inverted surfaces */

  /* Text */
  --text-primary: #000000;
  --text-secondary: rgba(0,0,0,0.64);   /* 64% black */
  --text-tertiary: rgba(0,0,0,0.48);    /* 48% black */
  --text-disabled: rgba(0,0,0,0.32);    /* 32% black */

  /* Semantic */
  --color-accent: #006657;       /* Teal-900 */
  --color-positive: #006657;     /* Teal-900 */
  --color-warning: #B89F00;      /* Yellow-700 */
  --color-negative: #CE293F;     /* Red-600 */

  /* Accent backgrounds */
  --bg-accent: #E1FEFA;          /* Teal-100 */
  --bg-positive: #E1FEFA;        /* Teal-100 */
  --bg-warning: #FFFCE9;         /* Yellow-100 */
  --bg-negative: #FFEBED;        /* Red-100 */

  /* Brand primaries */
  --teal-primary: #00E5C4;       /* Teal-600 */
  --teal-dark: #006657;          /* Teal-900 */
  --teal-light: #E1FEFA;         /* Teal-100 */
  --red-primary: #FF334E;        /* Red-500 */
  --yellow-primary: #FFE11F;     /* Yellow-500 */
  --purple-primary: #7517E6;     /* Purple-500 */

  /* Borders */
  --border-primary: rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  --border-accent: #B2FCF1;      /* Teal-300 */
  --border-negative: #FFADB8;    /* Red-300 */
  --border-warning: #FFF3A5;     /* Yellow-300 */

  /* Elevation */
  --shadow-sm: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  --shadow-md: 0 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  --shadow-lg: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);

  /* Radii */
  --radius-xs: 8px;
  --radius-sm: 12px;
  --radius-md: 16px;
  --radius-lg: 20px;
  --radius-full: 999px;

  /* Spacing (8pt grid) */
  --space-4: 4px;
  --space-8: 8px;
  --space-12: 12px;
  --space-16: 16px;
  --space-20: 20px;
  --space-24: 24px;
  --space-32: 32px;
  --space-40: 40px;
  --space-48: 48px;

  /* Overlay */
  --overlay: rgba(0,0,0,0.60);
}
```

### Dark Mode

```css
[data-theme="dark"] {
  --bg-primary: #000000;         /* Neutral-1000 */
  --bg-secondary: #1F1F1F;       /* Neutral-900 */
  --bg-tertiary: #333333;        /* Neutral-800 */
  --bg-alt: #FFFFFF;

  --text-primary: #FFFFFF;
  --text-secondary: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
  --text-tertiary: rgba(255,255,255,0.48);
  --text-disabled: rgba(255,255,255,0.32);

  --color-accent: #33F6D8;       /* Teal-500 */
  --color-warning: #FFED79;      /* Yellow-400 */
  --color-negative: #FF7083;     /* Red-400 */

  --bg-accent: #072C28;          /* Teal-1000 */
  --bg-warning: #332D06;         /* Yellow-1000 */
  --bg-negative: #330007;        /* Red-1000 */

  --border-primary: rgba(255,255,255,0.16);
  --border-accent: #098669;      /* Teal-800 */
  --border-negative: #781624;    /* Red-800 */
}
```

### Mobile Phone Frame (for prototype presentation)

All prototypes rendering as mobile screens should use this wrapper pattern:

```
Frame width: 390px (iPhone 15 logical width)
Content padding: 16px horizontal
Status bar height: 54px (with time, signal, battery)
Bottom nav height: 84px + 34px home indicator = 118px
Safe content area: 390 x ~726px (between status bar and bottom nav)
```

