## Typography

**Font Family:** Baton Turbo
**Letter Spacing:** Negative tracking across all styles (typically -1 to -3)

All weights use Medium (600) for Display, Headline, Title, and Label. Body uses Regular (400).

### Base / Desktop (>1024px)

| Style | Size | Line Height | Weight |
|---|---|---|---|
| Display Lg | 88px | 96px | Medium (600) |
| Display Md | 60px | 72px | Medium (600) |
| Display Sm | 44px | 52px | Medium (600) |
| Headline Lg | 36px | 44px | Medium (600) |
| Headline Md | 28px | 36px | Medium (600) |
| Headline Sm | 24px | 32px | Medium (600) |
| Title Lg | 20px | 28px | Medium (600) |
| Title Md | 18px | 24px | Medium (600) |
| Title Sm | 16px | 24px | Medium (600) |
| Label Lg | 14px | 20px | Medium (600) |
| Label Md | 12px | 18px | Medium (600) |
| Label Sm | 10px | 16px | Medium (600) |
| Body XL | 18px | 27px | Regular (400) |
| Body Lg | 16px | 24px | Regular (400) |
| Body Md | 14px | 20px | Regular (400) |
| Body Sm | 12px | 18px | Regular (400) |

### Tablet (<1024px) — Responsive Overrides

Only Display and Headline sizes change. Title, Label, and Body remain the same.

| Style | Size | Line Height |
|---|---|---|
| Display Lg | 60px | 72px |
| Display Md | 44px | 52px |
| Display Sm | 36px | 44px |
| Headline Lg | 36px | 44px |
| Headline Md | 28px | 36px |
| Headline Sm | 24px | 32px |

### Mobile (<480px) — Responsive Overrides

| Style | Size | Line Height |
|---|---|---|
| Display Lg | 44px | 52px |
| Display Md | 36px | 44px |
| Display Sm | 28px | 36px |
| Headline Lg | 28px | 36px |
| Headline Md | 24px | 32px |
| Headline Sm | 24px | 32px |

### Prototype Type Usage Guide

For mobile prototypes, common mappings:

| UI Element | MLDS Style | CSS |
|---|---|---|
| Screen title | Headline Md (mobile) | 24px / 32px / 600 |
| Section header | Title Lg | 20px / 28px / 600 |
| Card title | Title Sm | 16px / 24px / 600 |
| Body text | Body Lg | 16px / 24px / 400 |
| Secondary text | Body Md | 14px / 20px / 400 |
