## Animation

| Type | Duration | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Micro-interactions | 100-150ms | Button press, toggle, checkbox |
| Panels and expands | 200-300ms | Accordions, drawers, bottom sheets |
| Closing | Faster than opening | Always |
| Easing | Never linear | Except progress bars |
| Reduced motion | Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` | Required |

---

## Accessibility

| Standard | Requirement |
|---|---|
| Text contrast | 4.5:1 minimum (WCAG AA) |
| Body text min size | 16px |
| Color-only meaning | Never. Pair with icon, text, or position |
| Touch targets | 44x44px (iOS) / 48x48dp (Android) |
| Loading states | Skeleton screens, not spinners |
| Focus indicators | Visible focus ring on all interactive elements |
| Screen readers | All interactive elements need accessible labels |

